data.description: Discover the charm of this cozy 3 bedroom home just minutes from downtown Brighton! Being located on a private paved drive, you can sit in the 10x20ft sunroom and enjoy a quiet setting while still being close to all Brighton has to offer.  Your new home was remodeled in 2016 and includes all new appliances, a detached 1 car garage, as well as a new roof, well pump, and energy efficient Boiler system! In the summer, enjoy nearby access to Woodland Lake and the boat ramp across the road!
